looking great today.

277
00:15:47,905 --> 00:15:50,531
Much better, much better!

278
00:15:51,909 --> 00:15:53,201
Get well soon !

279
00:15:55,037 --> 00:15:56,245
Oh !

280
00:15:56,330 --> 00:15:57,830
So, where is Jewel?

